{"tid":1403632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於剛才見到有市民今日設自助形式的物資站","createTime":"2019-08-03T20:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T03:36:46.000Z","uid":208452,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6c57f8b6c7738f103a9dc4dd36934d069059bb79","tid":1403632,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:14:53.000Z","msg":"大家好, 我地係香港自由之書, <br />\n曾經發起街站收集同派發現金券,八達通的一班人<br />\n<br />\n首先容我地澄清我地今日無擺街站亦無設立任何自取點<br />\n亦沒有以自助形式擺放任何物資供年輕手足自行領取<br />\n我地只係搵左人同團體幫手買物資落埸派/親手轉贈現金券<br />\n我地相信係有熱心市民自發設立<br />\n<br />\n我地唔抗拒任何團體/組織自發收集及親自派發物資比落埸的朋友<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔想做大台, 亦唔會做大台, 唔需要一定經我地捐</span></span><br />\n但我地唔建議亦<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔希望以自助形式</span></span><br />\n因為最<span style=\"color: red;\">需要的朋友佢地係唔會願意自己去拎</span>,<br />\n就連你親身派比佢都唔願收的時候,你寄望佢會自己去拎? 無可能<br />\n希望熱心的市民親手, 係親手交物資比出黎夢遊的朋友<br />\n你地用自助形式只會益左無需要的人, 幫唔係年輕朋友<br />\n<br />\n我地原意只係想解決佢地食的問題, 慳返筆錢去課裝備,<br />\n你地咁樣自助係唔會去到需要的人的手.....<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再次希望市民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再以自助形式收集同派發物資</span></span>.. </span></span><br />\n我真係唔想變左係其他手足口中的贖罪券,亦無左我地的原意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OOpD00E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOOpD00E.png&h=c097dea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖片由網友轉發比我地"},{"pid":"ea17122612daf5fe182edded2d76976a38316dd5","tid":1403632,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:17:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位手足如果見到以上情況煩請收集完落前線親手轉贈... 唔好益左班無需要的人...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80043d8a5ef449bf141c1ef855c0c6c7577d0c0","tid":1403632,"uid":34063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:23:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbe5721f8f06e76c41b4d5749f6f8cf94a646e5d","tid":1403632,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b43929cf96be38c8c8a4aeab108aee66ecfafcd","tid":1403632,"uid":182195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:29:39.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n次次都見到好多唔關事嘅人會收走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係幫緊前線"},{"pid":"ba307b39c30e8ecd1b3bc6abb76f31f5263d45df","tid":1403632,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea60c5df9606cf48307389a00fb1c1bf8758e05d","tid":1403632,"uid":37226,"like":0,"disli